*Galax urceolata* (Poir.) Brummitt
det. Michelle L. Gaynor (FLAS)        2024

SOUTH CAROLINA
Pickens County

*Galax aphylla* L.

Typical granite out crop vegetation but along streams there
were very grassy gladey area with *Chionanthus*, french
mulberry, red cedar with a large American ash dom. the
canopy. Rachel Creek drains the western extreme of Pinnacle
Mtn. 35.0195N & 82.7344W.

Bert Pittman 06110310
Ann Darr       2484                11 June 2003
